WEBVTT

00:06:28.462 --> 00:06:33.444
Or like Mr. W -- he likes
to go out every day,

00:06:33.468 --> 00:06:36.084
see if there are nice ladies around.

00:06:36.108 --> 00:06:38.096
(Laughter)

00:06:38.465 --> 00:06:40.020
And he's very courteous to them,

00:06:40.044 --> 00:06:42.545
and he hopes for smiles and he gets them.

00:06:42.863 --> 00:06:45.196
And he dances with them in the pub.

00:06:46.014 --> 00:06:47.530
It's a feast every day.

00:06:47.554 --> 00:06:50.768
There are people that would
rather go to the restaurant,

00:06:50.792 --> 00:06:52.466
have a wine with friends,

00:06:52.490 --> 00:06:56.156
or lunch or dinner with friends
and celebrate life.

00:06:56.180 --> 00:06:58.966
And my mother,
she takes a walk in the park,

00:06:58.990 --> 00:07:00.673
and sits on a bench in the sun,